Reviewing CO-474 provider-worker handoff readiness.

Findings:
- [P1] Treating review_outcome=clean-success as clean loses actionable review findings
  Raw standalone review output already reported actionable findings, but the paired telemetry surface let downstream handoff summarize the review as clean.
- [P2] Provider-worker handoff omits parsed finding evidence
  Workpad and operator summaries need machine-readable finding count and severity evidence before calling a review clean.
